    "desc": "After failure to further modernize the F11 chassis, the F16 was instead chosen to mount the new Y-110 cannon. The turret was replaced with a much heavier design intended for future proofing against potential threats. The hull was given a much cheaper upgrade, by simply bolting some additional angled armor to the front.",
